name: Vortex
description: Digital token of physical piece of art handmade by Metakupol (metakupol.com) @Metakupol -- Representing the Water element and linked to The Sacral Chakra the Icosahedron is the last in the series of the five Platonic Solids. Structurally made from twenty faces, twelve vertices and thirty edges. Transformation is the core of Icosahedron and would help energetically removing emotional blocks and would enhance the creativity allowing freedom of expression and positive change.
